{"ID":"20260305082131-aqd981x","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"custom-author":"[[[m0_64115130]]]","custom-created":"2026-01-07 00:00:00 +0000 UTC","custom-description":"文章浏览阅读2.6k次，点赞25次，收藏16次。本手册适用于有一定JavaScript基础的、学习HarmonyOS开发的初学者，另外还有配套练习提供给初学者使用。TypeScript（简称 TS）是微软公司开发的一种基于 JavaScript （简称 JS）语言的编程语言。TypeScript 可以看成是 JavaScript 的超集（superset），即它继承了后者的全部语法，并为此基础上做出了一定的修改。学习TypeScript注意区分与JavaScript的区别。_use explicit types instead of \u0026quot;any\u0026quot;, \u0026quot;unknown\u0026quot; (arkts-no-any-unknown)","custom-published":"2024-06-24 00:00:00 +0000 UTC","custom-source":"https://blog.csdn.net/m0_64115130/article/details/139927257","id":"20260305082131-aqd981x","tags":"clippings","title":"＜HarmonyOS＞ArkTS语法手册【更新中...】","type":"doc","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082201-p0hns9p","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","Properties":{"id":"20260305082201-p0hns9p"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"eWFtbA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"---\ntitle: \"＜HarmonyOS＞ArkTS语法手册【更新中...】\"\nsource: \"https://blog.csdn.net/m0_64115130/article/details/139927257\"\nauthor:\n  - \"[[m0_64115130]]\"\npublished: 2024-06-24\ncreated: 2026-01-07\ndescription: \"文章浏览阅读2.6k次，点赞25次，收藏16次。本手册适用于有一定JavaScript基础的、学习HarmonyOS开发的初学者，另外还有配套练习提供给初学者使用。TypeScript（简称 TS）是微软公司开发的一种基于 JavaScript （简称 JS）语言的编程语言。TypeScript 可以看成是 JavaScript 的超集（superset），即它继承了后者的全部语法，并为此基础上做出了一定的修改。学习TypeScript注意区分与JavaScript的区别。_use explicit types instead of \\\"any\\\", \\\"unknown\\\" (arkts-no-any-unknown)\"\ntags:\n  - \"clippings\"\n---"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-veea7bi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-veea7bi","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\u003c HarmonyOS \u003eArkTS语法手册"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-kpq0mrh","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-kpq0mrh","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"前言"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-oy80pkn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-oy80pkn","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"本手册适用于有一定 JavaScript 基础的、学习HarmonyOS开发的初学者，另外还有配套练习提供给初学者使用。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-vrokm5p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-vrokm5p","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"编译器环境： "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://developer.huawei.com/consumer/cn/download/","TextMarkATitle":"devecostudio-windows-5.0.3.403","TextMarkTextContent":"devecostudio-windows-5.0.3.403"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-fy15gwf","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-fy15gwf","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"TypeScript语法部分"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-mhoj2vu","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-mhoj2vu","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"简介"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-fgqiz8u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-fgqiz8u","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"TypeScript（简称 TS）是微软公司开发的一种基于 JavaScript （简称 JS）语言的编程语言。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-xywlc2m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-xywlc2m","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"TypeScript 可以看成是 JavaScript 的超集（superset），即它继承了后者的全部语法，并为此基础上做出了一定的修改。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-fibwcq3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-fibwcq3","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"学习TypeScript注意区分与JavaScript的区别"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-zjxnxal","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-zjxnxal","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.类型"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-3yjd9no","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-3yjd9no","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.1类型的概念"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-2u5r246","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-2u5r246","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"类型（type）指的是一组具有相同特征的值。如果两个值具有某种共同的特征，就可以说，它们属于同一种类型。举例来说， "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"123"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 和 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"456"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 这两个值，共同特征是都能进行数值运算，所以都属于“数值”（number）这个类型。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-jtywe62","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-jtywe62","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"类型主要目的是在软件开发过程中，为编译器和开发工具提供更多的验证和帮助，帮助提高代码质量，减少错误。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-f23l6x1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-f23l6x1","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对此TypeScript和JavaScript重要的区别一点在于："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-dt9oyd4","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-dt9oyd4","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-sm4jhky","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-sm4jhky","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-ffjyg64","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ffjyg64","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"JavaScript 代码编辑时（开发阶段）不会检查类型对不对，只在运行后显示错误。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-8kjz7bo","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-8kjz7bo","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-yprde3j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-yprde3j","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"TypeScript是在开发阶段报错，这样有利于提早发现错误，避免使用时报错。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-blvacmo","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-blvacmo","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.2类型分类"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-i5xo4o0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-i5xo4o0","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"动态类型和静态类型是编程语言中的两种类型检查机制，它们主要区别在于 数据类型 检查和确定的时机。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-1hkgp2s","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-1hkgp2s","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"##### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"动态类型"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-49d0kzz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-49d0kzz","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在静态类型语言中，变量的数据类型在编译时就已经确定，并且在后续的代码执行中不会改变。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-23hf590","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-23hf590","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"JavaScript语言就是用的是动态类型。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-vo9557p","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-vo9557p","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"##### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"静态类型"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-uwngy3n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-uwngy3n","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在动态类型语言中，变量的数据类型是在运行时确定的，也就是说，变量可以存储任何类型的值，直到它被实际赋值之前，它的类型是未知的。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-g2cs6d4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-g2cs6d4","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"TypeScript就是用的是静态类型。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ohtztwj","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":6,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ohtztwj","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"###### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"静态类型的缺点："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-s4eeulu","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-s4eeulu","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-e2qdgh7","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-e2qdgh7","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-4wdgnhj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-4wdgnhj","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"丧失了动态类型的代码灵活性。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-kc36r01","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-kc36r01","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-vf5o0h2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-vf5o0h2","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"增加了编程工作量。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-hzzq292","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"3.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":3,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-hzzq292","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-4v3im8d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-4v3im8d","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"更高的学习成本。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-nq6zsd8","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"4.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":4,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"NC4=","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-nq6zsd8","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-hhckngf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-hhckngf","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"引入了独立的编译步骤。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-2vn94r5","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"5.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":5,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"NS4=","Num":5},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-2vn94r5","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-gyk6f3z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-gyk6f3z","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兼容性问题。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-sag32ex","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":6,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-sag32ex","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"###### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"静态类型的优点："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-751rkvo","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-751rkvo","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-vp7vprd","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-vp7vprd","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-dsxhmyj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-dsxhmyj","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有利于代码的静态分析。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-vq6tkgx","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-vq6tkgx","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-teje7g7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-teje7g7","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有利于发现错误。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-h258qfx","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"3.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":3,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-h258qfx","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-68szpl8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-68szpl8","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"更好的 IDE 支持，做到语法提示和自动补全。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ky3trb4","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"4.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":4,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"NC4=","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ky3trb4","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-g2rdz23","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-g2rdz23","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"提供了代码文档。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-qd3apv9","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"5.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":5,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"NS4=","Num":5},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-qd3apv9","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-89hwujj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-89hwujj","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有助于代码重构。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-f40fqic","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-f40fqic","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.3类型声明"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-m0f0s5j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-m0f0s5j","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"TypeScript 代码最明显的特征，就是为 JavaScript 变量加上了类型声明。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-t0utbnh","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-t0utbnh","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"let str:string = '你好' \n\nlet num:number = 123\n\nconsole.log(str,num) // 你好 123\n\n \n\n//示例中，变量名str的后面使用冒号，声明了它的类型为string\n\n//变量名num则声明了它的类型为number。\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-dlr9596","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-dlr9596","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"注意，变量的值应该与声明的类型一致，如果不一致，TypeScript 就会报错。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-grcyip3","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-grcyip3","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"let str:string = 123; //报错\n\n//示例中，变量str类型是字符串，但是赋值的是数字，因此报错\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-dm1k29b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-dm1k29b","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"另外，TypeScript 规定，变量只有赋值后才能使用，否则就会报错。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-begfmvg","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-begfmvg","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"let str:number \n\nconsole.log(str) //报错\n\n//示例中，变量str没有赋值就被读取，导致报错。\n\n//而 JavaScript 允许这种行为，不会报错，没有赋值的变量会输出undefined\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-afjt5ha","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-afjt5ha","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.4类型推断"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-jefo8wy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-jefo8wy","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"类型声明并不是必需的，如果没有，TypeScript 会自己推断类型。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-dmfq0s5","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-dmfq0s5","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"let num = 123 \n\nconsole.log(num) //123\n\n//示例中，变量str没有类型声明，TypeScript就会自动判断它的类型。\n\n//由于它被赋值为一个数值，因此 TypeScript 推断它的类型为number。\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-2csdeum","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-2csdeum","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果变量 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"num"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 更改为其他类型的值，跟推断的类型不一致，TypeScript 就会报错。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-4xttlmg","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-4xttlmg","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"let num = 123\n\nnum = 'hello'  // 报错\n\n//示例中，变量num的类型推断为number，后面赋值为字符串，TypeScript 就报错了。\njavascript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-i7n2e3m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-i7n2e3m","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"TypeScript 也可以推断函数的返回值。将会在函数一节讲解。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-59kbtp6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-59kbtp6","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"总结："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" TypeScript 的设计思想是，类型声明是可选的，你可以加，也可以不加。即使不加类型声明，依然是有效的 TypeScript 代码，只是这时不能保证 TypeScript 会正确推断出类型。由于这个原因，所有 JavaScript 代码都是合法的 TypeScript 代码。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-v1z05l8","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-v1z05l8","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.5值和类型"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-bljbodn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-bljbodn","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"关系：“类型”是针对“值”的，可以视为是后者的一个元属性。每一个值在 TypeScript 里面都是有类型的。比如， "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"3"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 是一个值，它的类型是 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"number"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-qbqmpyb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-qbqmpyb","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"TypeScript 代码只涉及类型，不涉及值。所有跟“值”相关的处理，都由 JavaScript 完成。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-6drho7q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-6drho7q","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"因此：一种是底层的“值代码”，另一种是上层的“类型代码”。前者使用 JavaScript 语法，后者使用 TypeScript 的类型语法。TypeScript 的编译过程，实际上就是把“类型代码”全部拿掉，只保留“值代码”。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-n7uk87i","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-n7uk87i","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.6TypeScript 的编译原理"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-1l5li4b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-1l5li4b","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"JavaScript 的运行环境（浏览器和 Node.js）不认识 TypeScript 代码。所以，TypeScript 项目要想运行，必须先转为 JavaScript 代码，这个代码转换的过程就叫做“编译”。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-k9b577c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-k9b577c","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"TypeScript 官方没有做运行环境，只提供编译器。编译时，会将类型声明和类型相关的代码全部删除，只留下能运行的 JavaScript 代码，并且不会改变 JavaScript 的运行结果。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-3r652ng","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-3r652ng","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"因此，TypeScript 的类型检查只是编译时的类型检查，而不是运行时的类型检查。一旦代码编译为 JavaScript，运行时就不再检查类型了。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-1r3zexl","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-1r3zexl","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.TypeScript 的类型系统"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-6gmjc31","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-6gmjc31","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"TypeScript 继承了 JavaScript 的类型，在这个基础上，定义了一套自己的类型系统。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-hwuva16","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-hwuva16","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.1基本类型"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-1fqucgo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-1fqucgo","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"JavaScript数据类型有8种：number、string、boolean、undefined、null、symbol、bigint、object"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ld6k2f3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ld6k2f3","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"TypeScript继承了JavaScript的数据类型，除了object类型其他依然称为基本类型。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-vvk4m9t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-vvk4m9t","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"除了8种类型，TypeScript新增了以下类型："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-mbe6khu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-mbe6khu","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"元组、泛型、枚举类型、any 类型，unknown 类型，never 类型、接口类型、值类型、联合类型、交叉类型。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-xlgtnem","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-xlgtnem","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"注意："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 上面所有类型的名称都是小写字母，首字母大写的 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"Number"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 、 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"String"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 、 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"Boolean"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 等在 JavaScript 语言中都是内置对象，而不是类型名称。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-fndortu","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-fndortu","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"//JavaScript中的首字母大写的Number、String、Boolean作为内置函数使用，强制转换功能\n\n//另外还可以作为包装对象 \n\nconsole.log(Number('456')) //456\n\nconsole.log(String(123)) //'123'\n\nconsole.log(Boolean(1)) //true\njavascript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-khyg1mp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-khyg1mp","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"另外，undefined 和 null 既可以作为值，也可以作为类型，取决于在哪里使用它们。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-l8pjuc9","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-l8pjuc9","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"//作为值\n\nlet x;\n\nconsole.log(x) // 输出 undefined\n\nlet y = null\n\nconsole.log(y) // 输出 null\n\n \n\n//作为类型\n\nlet a: undefined | string //变量a被定义为可以接受 undefined 或 string 类型的值\n\na = \"Hello\"; // 这是合法的\n\n \n\nlet b: null | number //变量b被定义为可以接受 null 或 number 类型的值\n\nb = 123; // 这也是合法的\njavascript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-xx98yiz","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-xx98yiz","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"##### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.1.1number、string、boolean、null、undefined类型"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-eww7dco","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-eww7dco","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"// number类型\n\nlet num1:number = 123\n\nlet num2:number = 3.14\n\nlet num3:number = 0xffff //16进制\n\nlet num4:number = 0o15 //8进制\n\nconsole.log(num1,num2,num3,num4) //123 3.14 65535 13\n\n \n\n \n\n// string类型\n\nlet str1:string = \"hello\"\n\nlet str2:string = 'world' //单引号和双引号都可以使用，但是不能混用。\n\nlet str3:string = \\`${str1} ${str2}\\` //模板字符串，可以包含换行符和变量。\n\nconsole.log(str1,str2,str3) //hello world hello world\n\n \n\n// boolean类型\n\nlet bool1:boolean = true //true或false，区分大小写。\n\nlet bool2:boolean = false //true或false，区分大小写。\n\nconsole.log(bool1,bool2) //true false\n\n \n\n// null和undefined类型\n\nlet n:null = null //null，表示空值（即此处没有值）。\n\nlet u:undefined = undefined //undefined，表示未定义(即还未给出定义，以后可能会有定义。两个undefined里面，第一个是类型，第二个是值。）。\n\nconsole.log(n,u) //null undefined\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-nv1m7lc","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-nv1m7lc","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"##### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.1.2object类型"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-065njba","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-065njba","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"let x:object = { foo: 123 }\n\nlet y:object = [1, 2, 3]\n\nlet z:object = (n:number) =\u003e n + 1\n\n//上面示例中，对象、数组、函数都属于 object 类型。\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-4hlkh0r","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-4hlkh0r","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.2undefined和null的特殊性"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-quncspd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-quncspd","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"undefined"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 和 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"null"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 既是值，又是类型。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-73uz9wh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-73uz9wh","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"作为值，它们有一个特殊的地方：任何其他类型的变量都可以赋值为 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"undefined"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 或 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"null"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-5k55x53","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-5k55x53","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.3值类型"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-39ibbdj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-39ibbdj","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"TypeScript 规定，单个值也是一种类型，称为“值类型”。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-55cc289","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-55cc289","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"//值类型\n\nlet x:'type'\n\nx = 'type' //类型为'type'。\n\nx = 'other' //报错，类型不是'type'。\n\n//变量x的类型是字符串type，导致它只能赋值为这个字符串，赋值为其他字符串就会报错。\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-qywfk5d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-qywfk5d","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"推断类型时，遇到 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"const**关键字**"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 声明的变量，如果代码里面没有注明类型，就会推断该变量是值类型。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-kwci7fs","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-kwci7fs","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"const a = 'type' //a的类型为'type'。\n\nconst b:string = 'type' //b的类型为string。\n\n//示例中，变量a是const命令声明的，TypeScript 就会推断它的类型是值type，而不是string类型。\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ohwy0xw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ohwy0xw","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"const"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 关键字声明的变量，如果赋值为对象，并不会推断为值类型。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-cucgjs5","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-cucgjs5","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"// x 的类型是 { foo: number }\n\nconst x = { foo: 1 }\n\n//示例中，变量x没有被推断为值类型，而是推断属性foo的类型是number。这是因为 JavaScript 里面，const变量赋值为对象时，属性值是可以改变的。\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-lmwi20n","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-lmwi20n","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.4联合类型(union types)"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-nheazc9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-nheazc9","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"联合类型（union types）指的是多个类型组成的一个新类型，使用符号 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"|"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 表示。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-47r9tya","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-47r9tya","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"联合类型 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"A|B"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 表示，任何一个类型只要属于 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"A"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 或 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"B"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ，就属于联合类型 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"A|B"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-r2fcd5k","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-r2fcd5k","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"let x:string|number\n\n \n\nx = 123  // 正确\n\nx = 'abc'  // 正确\n\n//示例中，变量x就是联合类型string|number，表示它的值既可以是字符串，也可以是数值。\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-c7j53q8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-c7j53q8","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"联合类型里面除了基本类型可以是其他任一类型组合。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-4s1dahk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-4s1dahk","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"联合类型的第一个成员前面，也可以加上竖杠 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"|"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ，这样便于多行书写。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-w7e9aom","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-w7e9aom","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"let x:\n\n  | 'one'\n\n  | 'two'\n\n  | 'three'\n\n  | 'four'\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-x597cqv","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-x597cqv","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.5交叉类型(ArkTS删除该语法)"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-d611mn6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-d611mn6","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"交叉类型（intersection types）指的多个类型组成的一个新类型，使用符号 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"\u0026amp;"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 表示。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-mcr5omf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-mcr5omf","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"交叉类型 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"A\u0026amp;B"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 表示，任何一个类型必须同时属于 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"A"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 和 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"B"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ，才属于交叉类型 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"A\u0026amp;B"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ，即交叉类型同时满足 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"A"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 和 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"B"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的特征。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-j6a3nee","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-j6a3nee","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"let x:number\u0026string\n\n//示例中，变量x同时是数值和字符串，这当然是不可能的，所以 TypeScript 会认为x的类型实际是never。\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ao8c9mb","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ao8c9mb","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.6 type 命令"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-yzejuix","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-yzejuix","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"type"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 命令用来定义一个类型的别名。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-rsrrade","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-rsrrade","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"type Age = number\n\n \n\nlet age:Age = 55\n\n//示例中，type命令为number类型定义了一个别名Age。这样就能像使用number一样，使用Age作为类型。\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-m3yifcl","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-m3yifcl","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e "},{"ID":"20260305082131-li8qqda","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-li8qqda","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"优点：可以让类型的名字变得更有意义，也能增加代码的可读性，还可以使复杂类型用起来更方便，便于以后修改变量的类型。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-2pots99","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-2pots99","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"特点："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-frl3cej","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-frl3cej","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-tbb1qd3","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-tbb1qd3","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-c8nhq1s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-c8nhq1s","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"别名不允许重名。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-odi8chb","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-odi8chb","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-x11vvmz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-x11vvmz","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"别名的作用域是块级作用域。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-fb7r038","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-fb7r038","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-842kqdb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-842kqdb","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"别名支持使用表达式，也可以在定义一个别名时，使用另一个别名，即别名允许嵌套。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-3u7tg7x","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-3u7tg7x","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"//别名不可以重复\n\ntype Color = 'red';\n\ntype Color = 'blue'; // 报错\n\n//示例中，同一个别名Color声明了两次，就报错了。\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-jr5ujsj","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-jr5ujsj","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"//别名的作用域是块级作用域\n\ntype Color = 'red'\n\n \n\nif (Math.random() \u003c 0.5) {\n\n  type Color = 'blue'\n\n}\n\n//示例中，if代码块内部的类型别名Color，跟外部的Color是不一样的。\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-1jknwlf","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-1jknwlf","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"//别名支持使用表达式，也可以在定义一个别名时，使用另一个别名，即别名允许嵌套。\n\ntype World = \"world\";\n\ntype Greeting = \\`hello ${World}\\`\n\n//示例中，别名Greeting使用了模板字符串，读取另一个别名World。\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-2ok89bt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-2ok89bt","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"type"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 命令属于类型相关的代码，编译成 JavaScript 的时候，会被全部删除。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-oygosvm","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-oygosvm","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.7 typeof 运算符"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ordffyn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ordffyn","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"JavaScript 语言中，typeof 运算符是一个一元运算符，返回一个字符串，代表操作数的类型。 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"typeof"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 运算符只可能返回八种结果，而且都是字符串。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-pe88eex","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-pe88eex","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"TypeScript 将 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"typeof"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 运算符移植到了类型运算，它的操作数依然是一个值，但是返回的不是字符串，而是该值的 TypeScript 类型。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-2k71mrs","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-2k71mrs","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"let a = 1;\n\nlet b:typeof a; //作为类型运算\n\n \n\nif (typeof a === 'number') { //作为表达式运算\n\n  b = a;\n\n}\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-5hmj38m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-5hmj38m","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"ArkTS仅支持在表达式中使用"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"typeof"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"运算符，不允许使用"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"typeof"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"作为类型。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-c7ansjr","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-c7ansjr","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.symbol类型"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-f2jgf2u","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-f2jgf2u","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4.数组"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-1ayzwy3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-1ayzwy3","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"JavaScript 数组在 TypeScript 里面分成两种类型，分别是数组（array）和元组（tuple）。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-2vonl6d","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-2vonl6d","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4.1数组"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-vpy9b3h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-vpy9b3h","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"数组的类型有两种写法。第一种写法是在数组成员的类型后面，加上一对方括号。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-3kjah76","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-3kjah76","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"//一维数组\n\nlet arr:number[] = [1,2,3] //数组类型，元素类型为number。\n\n//如果数组成员的类型比较复杂，可以写在圆括号里面。\n\nlet arr:(number|string)[]\n\n \n\n//多维数组\n\nlet multi:number[][] = [[1,2,3], [23,24,25]]\n\n//示例中，变量multi的类型是number[][]，表示它是一个二维数组，最底层的数组成员类型是number。\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-fi9pq6r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-fi9pq6r","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"圆括号是必须的，否则因为竖杠 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"|"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的优先级低于 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"[]"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ，TypeScript 会把 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"number|string[]"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 理解成 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"number"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 和 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"string[]"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的联合类型。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-kwk28hy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-kwk28hy","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"TypeScript 允许使用方括号读取数组成员的类型。ArkTS现已不支持。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-4m4l3yg","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-4m4l3yg","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"type Names = string[];\n\ntype Name = Names[0]; //在ArkTS报错  arkts-no-aliases-by-index\n\nlet na: Name = 'Alice'\n\nconsole.log(typeof na)// string \nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-n64gj92","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-n64gj92","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"JavaScript 规定， "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"const"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 命令声明的数组变量是可以改变成员的。TypeScript 允许声明只读数组，方法是在数组类型前面加上 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"readonly"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 关键字。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-c6ywg8b","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-c6ywg8b","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"const arr2:readonly number[] = [0, 1];\n\narr2[1] = 2; // 报错\n\narr2.push(3); // 报错\n\n示例中，arr2是一个只读数组，删除、修改、新增数组成员都会报错。\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-xn06enz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-xn06enz","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"注意， "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"readonly"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 关键字不能与数组的泛型写法一起使用"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-dykxjuh","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-dykxjuh","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"// 报错\n\nconst arr:readonly Array\u003cnumber\u003e = [0, 1];\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-obb5sz4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-obb5sz4","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"TypeScript 提供了两个专门的泛型，用来生成只读数组的类型。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-7e64t5c","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-7e64t5c","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"const a1:ReadonlyArray\u003cnumber\u003e = [0, 1];\n\n \n\nconst a2:Readonly\u003cnumber[]\u003e = [0, 1];\n\n//示例中，泛型ReadonlyArray\u003cT\u003e和Readonly\u003cT[]\u003e都可以用来生成只读数组类型。\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-400fzdw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-400fzdw","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"两者尖括号里面的写法不一样:"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-cq3ocko","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-cq3ocko","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-wctm3pd","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-wctm3pd","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-sidrn0k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-sidrn0k","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"Readonly\u0026lt;T[]\u0026gt;"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的尖括号里面是整个数组（ "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"number[]"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ）"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-5jgjv4y","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-5jgjv4y","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-5mkk5yj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-5mkk5yj","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"ReadonlyArray\u0026lt;T\u0026gt;"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的尖括号里面是数组成员（ "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"number"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ）。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-k88l61x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-k88l61x","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"只读数组还有一种声明方法，就是使用“const 断言”。ArkTS现已不支持。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-dykvcmi","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-dykvcmi","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"const arr = [0, 1] as const;\n\n \n\narr[0] = [2]; // 报错 \n\n//示例中，as const告诉 TypeScript，推断类型时要把变量arr推断为只读数组，从而使得数组成员无法改变。\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-vw136v4","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-vw136v4","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4.2元组"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-rhaye3s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-rhaye3s","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"元组（tuple）是 TypeScript 特有的数据类型，JavaScript 没有单独区分这种类型。它表示成员类型可以自由设置的数组，即数组的各个成员的类型可以不同。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-90bwe0r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-90bwe0r","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"数组的成员类型写在方括号外面（number"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"["}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"]"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"），元组的成员类型是写在方括号里面（"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"["}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"number"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"]"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"）"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-0wkfb0v","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-0wkfb0v","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"// 数组\n\nlet a:number[] = [1];\n\n \n\n// 元组\n\nlet t:[number] = [1];\n\n//示例中，变量a和t的值都是[1]，但是它们的类型是不一样的。a是一个数组，成员类型number写在方括号外面；t是一个元组，成员类型number写在方括号里面。\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-y2iv3v2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-y2iv3v2","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"注意一 由于成员的类型可以不一样，所以元组必须明确声明每个成员的类型。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-vfdk21t","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-vfdk21t","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"const s:[string, string, boolean]\n\n  = ['a', 'b', true];\n\n//示例中，元组s的前两个成员的类型是string，最后一个成员的类型是boolean。\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-qjv1ebf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-qjv1ebf","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"注意二 使用元组时，必须明确给出类型声明，不能省略，否则 TypeScript 会把一个值自动推断为数组。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-6sz2wh7","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-6sz2wh7","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"// a 的类型被推断为 (number | boolean)[]\n\nlet a = [1, true]\n\n//示例中，变量a的值其实是一个元组，但是 TypeScript 会将其推断为一个联合类型的数组，即a的类型为(number | boolean)[]。所以，元组必须显式给出类型声明。\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-mvd8fyu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-mvd8fyu","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"注意三 元组成员的类型可以添加问号后缀（"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"?"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"），表示该成员是可选的。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-kz15bwh","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-kz15bwh","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"let a:[number, number?] = [1];\n\n//示例中，元组a的第二个成员是可选的，可以省略。\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-qmozvh5","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-qmozvh5","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5.对象"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-5fdp5ro","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-5fdp5ro","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对象是 JavaScript 最基本的数据结构。TypeScript 对于对象类型有很多规则。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-6tqshz4","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-6tqshz4","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5.1声明对象"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-7ydhelq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-7ydhelq","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"ArkTS删除了字面量创造对像方式 和type命令创造对象方式。只可以用class和interface命令的方式。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-yxtpxt5","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-yxtpxt5","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"//用interface的方式\n\ninterface MyObj {\n\n  x: number;\n\n  y: number;\n\n}\n\n \n\nconst obj:MyObj = { x: 1, y: 1 };\n\n \n\n//用class的方式\n\nclass C1 {\n\n  n: number = 0\n\n  s: string = ''\n\n}\n\n \n\nlet o1: C1 = {n: 42, s: 'foo'};\n\nlet o2: C1 = {n: 42, s: 'foo'};\n\nlet o3: C1 = {n: 42, s: 'foo'};\n\n \n\nlet oo: C1[] = [{n: 1, s: '1'}, {n: 2, s: '2'}];\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-aciv1cc","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-aciv1cc","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5.2可选属性"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ggtxz8l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ggtxz8l","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果某个属性是可选的（即可以忽略），需要在属性名后面加一个问号。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-j12cmdy","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-j12cmdy","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"interface MyObj {\n\n  x: number;\n\n  y?: number;\n\n  //等同于\n\n  //y?: number|undefined;\n\n}\n\n \n\n \n\nconst obj:MyObj = { x: 1 };\n\nconst obj1:MyObj = { x: 1 , y: undefined };\n\n//类型MyObj的可选属性y可以是字符串，也可以是undefined，即可选属性可以赋值为undefined。\n\n \n\n//用class的方式\n\nclass C1 {\n\n  n: number = 0\n\n  s?: string = ''\n\n}\n\n \n\nlet o1: C1 = {n: 42};\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-cmjwc7g","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-cmjwc7g","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5.3只读属性"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-nhqqse5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-nhqqse5","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"属性名前面加上 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"readonly"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 关键字，表示这个属性是只读属性，不能修改。只读属性只能在对象初始化期间赋值，此后就不能修改该属性。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ip6bb8b","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ip6bb8b","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"interface MyInterface {\n\n  readonly prop: number;\n\n}\n\n \n\nlet obj3:MyInterface = {prop:18}\n\nobj3.prop = 16 \n\n//prop属性是只读属性，不能修改它的值。\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-46ebtti","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-46ebtti","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"初始化带"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"readonly"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"字段的类在ArkTS不支持"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-vp0pgax","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-vp0pgax","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"interface Home {\n\n  readonly resident: { //在typescripts是可以的，但在ArkTS不支持\n\n    name: string;\n\n    age: number\n\n  };\n\n}\n\n \n\nconst h: Home = {\n\n  resident: {\n\n    name: 'Vicky',\n\n    age: 42\n\n  }\n\n};\n\n \n\nh.resident.age = 32; \nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-v2m1w2q","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-v2m1w2q","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"6.函数"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-pbnnny2","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-pbnnny2","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"6.1函数声明"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-6lfypy4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-6lfypy4","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"函数的类型声明，需要在声明函数时，给出参数的类型和返回值的类型"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-z8m8sms","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-z8m8sms","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"7.类"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-iyfe5ea","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-iyfe5ea","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"8.接口interface"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-0rdkxb5","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-0rdkxb5","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"9.泛型"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-s5f8fee","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-s5f8fee","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"10.枚举Enum"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ilpebi2","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ilpebi2","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"ArkTS语法部分"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-fc1sqhv","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-fc1sqhv","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.简介"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-4nntb85","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-4nntb85","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"ArkTS(方舟编程语言),是华为开发的一种语言, 在 TypeScript 语言的基础上, 增加了"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-6w15plo","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-6w15plo","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-o4u0gdx","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-o4u0gdx","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-rdwk29o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-rdwk29o","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"声明式 UI"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-juruktc","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-juruktc","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-wqfgmoa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-wqfgmoa","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"状态管理"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-vvls6ls","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-vvls6ls","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"等能力, 可以 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://so.csdn.net/so/search?q=快速开发\u0026spm=1001.2101.3001.7020","TextMarkATitle":"快速开发","TextMarkTextContent":"快速开发"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" OpenHarmony 和 HarmonyOS 应用;"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-bebg8do","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-bebg8do","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.1声明式UI"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-o56pwtc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-o56pwtc","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"ArkUI 框架提供给开发者两种开发方式：基于 ArkTS 的声明式开发范式和基于 JS 扩展 的类 Web 开发范式。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-n3iqoc8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-n3iqoc8","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"声明式和命令式都是编程编程范式。我们的ArkTS就是声明式开发范式"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-en8izp8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-en8izp8","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"什么是UI？"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-tqcspa0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-tqcspa0","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"UI就是用户界面，就是移动端屏幕预览页面。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-voft923","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-voft923","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.2状态管理"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-tr40r9s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-tr40r9s","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"声明式开发范式的核心思想是数据驱动 UI 变化，通过提供的状态进行数据管理，这里 状态管理指的是，管理数据发生变化时，框架能自动更新这些数据关联的最小范围的 UI"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-89pou91","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-89pou91","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.3编译器介绍"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-fyj3sjc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-fyj3sjc","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"DevEco Studio 是华为基于IntelliJ公司开源idea开发的软件，为华为鸿蒙操作系统（HarmonyOS）应用开发设计的一站式集成开发环境（IDE）。这个名字来源于“Developer”和“Ecosystem”的结合，强调它旨在为开发者提供一个高效、全面的开发平台，以构建HarmonyOS应用生态。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-5j0bm6c","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-5j0bm6c","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.4HarmonyOS SDK"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-rv9z50s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-rv9z50s","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"HarmonyOS SDK 是为了支撑 Harmony OS 应用开发而提供的一系列开放能力，包括 API 接口定义，资料文档，样例代码，基础工具包等。HarmonyOS SDK 是鸿蒙生态建设的 重要组成部分"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-06vrxbd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-06vrxbd","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们所说的api12一般指的是HarmonyOS SDK版本"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-b2or5t0","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-b2or5t0","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.5OpenHarmony"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-awm9wc9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-awm9wc9","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"OpenHarmony是华为开发的鸿蒙开源版本系统，后面捐给了深开鸿公司。 HarmonyOS是华为基于OpenHarmony继续开发闭源的商用版本系统。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-txkxea8","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-txkxea8","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.6ArkTS特点"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-yqzhy9d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-yqzhy9d","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"作为鸿蒙开发的主力语言，ArkTS具有如下的几个特点："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-wchjxxs","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-wchjxxs","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-qkn11u7","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-qkn11u7","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-8bia908","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-8bia908","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"开发效率高，编程体验好"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"想要完成一个手机端页面的设计如果使用传统的页面开发需要用到三种不同的技术:HTML、CSS、JS 开发体验不统一，而使用ArkTSy一种语言就可以完成传统页面开发三种技术所做的事情，具有更好的编程体验"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"首先ArkTS中集成了声明式的UI组件，并且可以直接调用对象方法的方式完成组件样式的设置，同时ArkTS中还提供了状态管理机制监听数据的变化，一旦数据发生变化会造成组件的重新渲染【类似于Vue中的响应式数据】"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-edrihx2","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-edrihx2","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-26u3dm6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-26u3dm6","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"运行效率高：得益于底层提供的方舟编译器"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-5m7uya6","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"3.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":3,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-5m7uya6","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-021515i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-021515i","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"多系统适配和接入能力：使用ArkTS编写的代码可以适配到不同的操作系统上"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-shebqvt","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"4.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":4,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"NC4=","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-shebqvt","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-3rhoeoz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-3rhoeoz","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"因为ArkTS本身是基于TypeScript，因此在学习ArkTS之前需要掌握TypeScript语言"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-xv6gcit","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-xv6gcit","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.ArkTs与TypeScript语法的不同"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-kelru0e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-kelru0e","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"官方文档原话：根据开发者的反馈以及更多实际场景的数据，我们将来可能进一步 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"缩小"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 不支持特性的范围。意味着ArkTS语法上还会修改，修改后我将尽力更新。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-yn5h988","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-yn5h988","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.1console.log()输出不同"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-9knlig2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-9knlig2","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在 ArkTS 中， "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"console.log"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的行为遵循 C/C++ 的 printf 风格的格式化规则，这意味着当你调用 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"console.log"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 时，你不仅需要提供要打印的变量，还需要提供一个格式字符串来描述如何打印这些变量。如果没有提供格式字符串，编译器或运行环境可能无法正确解析你的意图，从而导致编译错误。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-zcdml37","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-zcdml37","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当你添加一个空字符串 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"''"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 或任何字符串作为第一个参数，如 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"console.log(' ', a, b, c)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ，你实际上提供了一个合法的格式字符串（即使它只是一个空格或不携带任何格式信息）。这满足了 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"console.log"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的调用规范，因此不会触发编译错误。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-u875tq9","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-u875tq9","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"let num1:number = 123\n\nlet num3:number = 0xffff //16进制\n\nconsole.log(num1,num3) //报错\n\nconsole.log('',num1,num3) //123 65535 \n\nconsole.log('%d',num1,num3) //123 65535 \nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-5ve6tms","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-5ve6tms","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.2编译原理不同"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-8ptjh1j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-8ptjh1j","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"ArkTS语言中的ets文件将会被编译成方舟字节码文件，而TypeScript是把ts文件编译成JavaScript中的js文件运行。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-afzch5c","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-afzch5c","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.3禁用var关键字声明变量"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-p68e7t0","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-p68e7t0","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.4限制运算符的语义"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-7qosghb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-7qosghb","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.一元运算符 '+'、"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"-"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"和"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"~ 只能作用于数值类型"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-6q58leg","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-6q58leg","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"// ArkTS仅允许一元运算符用于数值类型，否则会发生编译时错误。与TypeScript不同，ArkTS不支持隐式将字符串转换成数值，必须进行显式转换。\n\nlet a = +5;    // 5（number类型）\n\nlet b = +'5';    // 编译时错误\n\nlet c = -5;    // -5（number类型）\n\nlet d = -'5';    // 编译时错误\n\nlet e = ~5;    // -6（number类型）\n\nlet f = ~'5';    // 编译时错误\n\nlet g = +'string'; // 编译时错误\n\n \n\nfunction returnTen(): string {\n\n  return '-10';\n\n}\n\n \n\nfunction returnString(): string {\n\n  return 'string';\n\n}\n\n \n\nlet x = +returnTen();  // 编译时错误arkts-no-polymorphic-unops\n\nlet y = +returnString(); // 编译时错误arkts-no-polymorphic-unops\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-b36wegu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-b36wegu","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"."}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 仅允许在表达式中使用 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"typeof"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 运算符"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-knvwjoc","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-knvwjoc","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"let n1 = 42;\n\nlet s1 = 'foo';\n\nconsole.log(typeof n1); // 'number'\n\nconsole.log(typeof s1); // 'string'\n\nlet n2: typeof n1 //报错 arkts-no-type-query\n\nlet s2: typeof s1 //报错 arkts-no-type-query\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-v1u9etu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-v1u9etu","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"."}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 逗号运算符"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":","},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"仅用在"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"for"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"循环语句中"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-2f26fn5","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-2f26fn5","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"//为了方便理解执行顺序，在ArkTS中，逗号运算符仅适用于\\`for\\`循环语句中。\n\n//注意与声明变量、函数参数传递时的逗号分隔符不同。\n\nfor (let i = 0, j = 0; i \u003c 10; ++i, j += 2) {\n\n  // ...\n\n}\n\n \n\nlet x = 0;\n\nx = (++x, x++); // 报错\\`arkts-no-comma-outside-loops\\`\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-89on6n8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-89on6n8","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4.不支持"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"is"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"运算符，必须使用"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"instanceof"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"和"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"as"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"进行类型保护"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-em7c9dp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-em7c9dp","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"."}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 部分支持展开运算符"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-vfavbm1","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-vfavbm1","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"//ArkTS仅支持使用展开运算符展开数组、\\`Array\\`的子类和\\`TypedArray\\`（例如\\`Int32Array\\`）。\n\n \n\n \n\nfunction foo(x: number, y: number, z: number) {\n\n  // ...\n\n}\n\n \n\nlet args: [number, number, number] = [0, 1, 2];\n\nfoo(...args);//报错arkts-no-spread\n\n \n\nlet point2d = { x: 1, y: 2 };\n\nlet point3d = { ...point2d, z: 3 }; //报错arkts-no-spread\n\n \n\n//仅支持使用在以下场景中：\n\n \n\n//1. 传递给剩余参数时 \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n//2. 复制一个数组到数组字面量 \n\n \n\nlet originalArray:number[] = [1, 2, 3];\n\nlet copiedArray = [...originalArray];\n\nconsole.log('',copiedArray)\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-e5x22g8","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-e5x22g8","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.5不支持delete、in运算符"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-52u923f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-52u923f","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"报错： "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"`arkts-no-in`"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" "},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"arkts-no-delete"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-kcthjk3","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-kcthjk3","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.6不支持"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"for.. in"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-l3aatak","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-l3aatak","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"//由于在ArkTS中，对象布局在编译时是确定的、并且不能在运行时被改变，所以不支持使用\\`for .. in\\`迭代//一个对象的属性。对于数组来说，可以使用常规的\\`for\\`循环。\n\nlet a: string[] = ['1.0', '2.0', '3.0'];\n\nfor (let i in a) { //报错 \\`arkts-no-for-in\\`\n\n  console.log(a[i]); \n\n}\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-1pfp5cp","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-1pfp5cp","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.7 不支持"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"with"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"语句"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-cb77k1r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-cb77k1r","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"报错 "},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"arkts-no-with"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-9kajfoo","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-9kajfoo","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.8 不支持交叉类型"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-e1yq5ef","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-e1yq5ef","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.9 不支持any和unknown类型"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-amv07fj","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-amv07fj","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.10不支持索引访问类型"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-7p7dez5","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-7p7dez5","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"//对象类型不可以使用方括号读取属性的类型。\n\n//用type命令声明数组\n\ntype MyTuple = [string, number, boolean]; //定义个一个名为MyTuple的类型，是数组类型\n\ntype TupleElement = MyTuple[1];//定义了另一个名为TupleElement的类型，通过索引访问定义为number类型。\n\n// 报错\\`arkts-no-aliases-by-index\\`\n\n \n\n \n\ntype StringArray = string[]; //定义了一个类型别名 StringArray，是个字符串数组的类型\n\ntype StringFromArray = StringArray[number]; //定义了另一个类型别名 StringFromArray，StringArray[number]看作是映射了所有可能的数字索引（即数组的下标）到 string 类型的元素上\n\n // 报错\\`arkts-no-aliases-by-index\\`\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-f4zqyrh","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-f4zqyrh","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.11不支持通过索引访问字段"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-40dugzl","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-40dugzl","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"//ArkTS不支持动态声明字段。只能访问已在类中声明或者继承可见的字段，访问其他字段将会造成编译时错误。\n\ninterface MyObj {\n\n  x: number;\n\n  y: number;\n\n}\n\n \n\nconst obj:MyObj = { x: 1, y: 1 };\n\nconsole.log('',obj[x]) //arkts-no-props-by-index\n\n \n\n \n\nclass Point {\n\n  x: string = ''\n\n  y: string = ''\n\n}\n\nlet p: Point = {x: '1', y: '2'};\n\nconsole.log(p['x']);  //arkts-no-props-by-index\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-pmmqmls","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-pmmqmls","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.12不支持"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"as const"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"断言"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-k0jfdbd","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-k0jfdbd","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.13对象字面量不能用于类型声明"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-4yikl2x","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-4yikl2x","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"dHlwZXNjcmlwdA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"//ArkTS不支持使用对象字面量声明类型，可以使用类或者接口声明类型。\n\ntype MyObj = {\n\n  x:number;\n\n  y:number;\n\n};\n\nconst o1:MyObj = { x: 1,y:2 }; //报错 \\`arkts-no-obj-literals-as-types\\`\n\n \n\nconst obj:{\n\n  x:number;\n\n  y:number;\n\n} = { x: 1, y: 1 }; //报错 \\`arkts-no-obj-literals-as-types\\`\nTypeScript\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-9rkbdqy","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-9rkbdqy","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.14 需要显式标注对象字面量的类型"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-rn6a5c5","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-rn6a5c5","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-0ekagdi","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-0ekagdi","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-me8fzy6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-me8fzy6","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"初始化不具有"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"any"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"、"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"`"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Object"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children"